Assignment 1
Questions:
Create a webpage with a title, a main heading,
and two paragraphs.

1.Add an image with a caption below it and
center both on the page.

2.Style all paragraphs with a different font
family, line height, and text alignment.

3.Design a styled button with padding, border,
and a hover effect.

4.Create a simple table with three columns and
three rows, and a basic form with two input
fields and a submit button.

HTML and CSS Code

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>HTML & CSS Assignment</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 30px;
      background-color: beige;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color:black;
    }

    /* Question 3: Paragraph styling */
    p {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      text-align: justify;
      color: black;
    }

    /* Question 2: Image & caption centered */
    .image-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .image-container img {
      max-width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .caption {
      font-style: italic;
      color: grey;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Question 4: Styled button */
    .styled-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid #2980b9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .styled-button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }

    /* Question 5: Table styling */
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    table, th, td {
      border: 1px solid #aaa;
    }

    th, td {
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Question 5: Form styling */
    form {
      margin-top: 30px;
      background-color: grey;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid grey;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Question 1: Title, Heading, Paragraphs -->
  <h1>Welcome to My Assignment Page</h1>

  <p>This is the first paragraph. It introduces the content of the page and welcomes visitors with a friendly tone.</p>
  <p>This is the second paragraph. It provides additional information and encourages the user to continue exploring the webpage.</p>

  <!-- Question 2: Image with caption centered -->
  <div class="image-container">
    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQTokxh8gi0P-ZoGgL4wTS3b-_MHq6a8a96uw&s" alt="Sample Image">
    <p class="caption">Michael Jordan.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Question 4: Styled Button -->
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <button class="styled-button">Click Me</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Question 5: Simple Table -->
  <h2>Sample Table</h2>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Age</th>
      <th>City</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Alice</td>
      <td>25</td>
      <td>New York</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Bob</td>
      <td>30</td>
      <td>London</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Charlie</td>
      <td>28</td>
      <td>Paris</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Question 5: Basic Form -->
  <h2>Contact Form</h2>
  <form>
    <label for="username">Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="username" name="username"><br><br>

    <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email"><br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="styled-button">
  </form>

</body>
</html>
